  <div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to <strong>Huntress</strong></h1>
      <p class="lead">The free job application tracking system.</p>
      <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-success btn-lg justify-content-center" role="button" aria-pressed="false" style="background-color: #01B2E5; border-color: white;">Join for Free</a>
    </div>
  </div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-6">
    <ul class="list-unstyled">
      <li class="media">
        <i class="fas fa-baby" style="padding: 3px 5px 0px 0px;"></i>
        <div class="media-body">
          <h5 class="mt-0 mb-1">Easy to use</h5>
          We do not have bloated features, only the necessities to enable easy tracking and organization of multiple jobs. You can focus on your job search without having to deal with a complex system and interface.
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="media my-4">
        <i class="fas fa-fire" style="padding: 3px 5px 0px 0px;"></i>
        <div class="media-body">
          <h5 class="mt-0 mb-1">Import from popular job sites</h5>
          Import a job directly from Indeed by pasting in the URL and hitting a button. We take care of the rest. Importing from other popular job boards will be added in the future.
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="media">
        <i class="far fa-money-bill-alt" style="padding: 4px 5px 0px 0px;"></i>
        <div class="media-body">
          <h5 class="mt-0 mb-1">No cost</h5>
          Track as many jobs as you like for free. Donations welcomed.
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <% if @jobs.count >= 3 %>
    <div class="col-sm-6">
      <h3>Recently added</h3>
      <div class="list-group">
        <% @jobs.each do |job| %>
          <div class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
            <div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between">
              <h5 class="mb-1"><%=job.title%></h5>
              <% if job.created_on != nil%>
                <small><%= job.created_on.strftime("%m/%d/%y %I:%M:%S %p")%></small>
              <% end %>
            </div>
            <p class="mb-1"><%=job.company%></p>
            <small><%=job.location%></small>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>

  <div class="text-center">
    <img src="https://i.imgur.com/k4eVnBx.png" class="thumbnail shadow-lg p-3 mb-5 bg-white rounded" alt="Responsive image" style="width:75%;">
  </div>